# FX Market Research agent — enables Claude-generated commentary + per-pair signals.
# Without it, live rates still load and signals fall back to a rule-based read.
# Get a key at https://console.anthropic.com → set the same var in Vercel project env.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# Enables LIVE data via Apify across all three research tabs:
#   FX:     gochujang/economic-calendar-tracker (ForexFactory calendar, free)
#           cloud9_ai/investing-news-scraper (Investing.com news, ~$0.002/headline)
#           xtracto/myfxbook-community-outlook (Myfxbook retail % long/short, ~$0.02/pair)
#   Crypto: gentle_cloud/cryptocurrency-market-data-scraper (CoinGecko, ~$0.001/coin)
#   Stocks: ryanclinton/finnhub-stock-data (needs FINNHUB_API_KEY below)
# Without the token, FX falls back to curated calendar / rule-based; Crypto and
# Stocks show a "needs token" notice.
# Get a token at https://console.apify.com/account/integrations
APIFY_TOKEN=apify_api_...

# Free Finnhub API key — required for the Stock Research tab (passed as the
# Finnhub Apify actor's `apiKey` input). Without it the Stock tab shows a notice.
# Get one free at https://finnhub.io/register
FINNHUB_API_KEY=...
